      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       spl-cls-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se errori : uscita                              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        p-rsc                not  = spaces
                     go to spl-cls-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
