      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Apertura file [stp] in output                             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       opo-stp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Open output                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-not-err            to   e-sts                  .
           open      output stp                                       .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Set dello status di errore se necessario        *
