                     move  e-sts          to   p-rsc                  .
       opo-stp-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Chiusura file [stp]                                       *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       cls-stp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-not-err            to   e-sts                  .
           close     stp                                              .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Set dello status di errore se necessario        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        e-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     move  e-sts          to   p-rsc                  .
       cls-stp-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Delete file [stp]                                         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       dlt-stp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      e-not-err            to   e-sts                  .
           delete    file   stp                                       .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Set dello status di errore se necessario        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        e-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     move  e-sts          to   p-rsc                  .
       dlt-stp-999.
